node.text:
Doyers Street in Chinatown got a colorful makeover - Tag a friend! 🌈🎨 This art is part of NYC’s “Asphalt Art Activations,” a program that commissions artists to paint large-scale murals on pedestrian public spaces. Swipe to see the bird’s eye view! #NYBucketlist
🎨: @dasicfernandez
📸: @girlintheyellowtaxinyc @mingomatic

node.text: Nothing but blue skies and ☀️ this weekend - who’s in for a boat day? 🛥We’ve rounded up the best ways to spend a day on the water in NYC. Find the full list at Bucketlisters.com or our link-in-bio 🎥 @elizabethfowlerx

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by New York Bucket List on July 23, 2021 tagging @eatalyflatiron, @nybucketlist, and @eatalydowntown. May be an image of indoor.

node.text: Who wants to experience an Italian summer at @eatalyflatiron & @eatalydowntown? 🥂🇮🇹🍝 From a scoop of housemade gelato or fresh pasta for a night in, to seasonal dishes at blooming rooftop Serra by Birreria, a refreshing Spritz at the piazza-inspired Il Patio di Eataly, & authentic Italian staples at La Pizza & La Pasta A Colori, there are so many ways to explore these two marketplaces. Check our link-in-bio for full details! #NYBucketlist #Partner
